<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Encurtador de URL</title>
        
        <meta name="description" content="Linkzin é um encurtador de URL usado para encurtar longos endereços de sites. Com o Linkzin é possível diminuir o tamanho do link criando uma url curta para compartilhar em outros locais, além de monitorar estatísticas de tráfego.">
        <meta name="keywords" content="Linkzin, linkzin, Encurtador, encurtador, linkzin encurtador, encurtador de link, encurtar link">
        <meta property="og:title" content="Linkzin - Encurtador de URL">
        <meta property="og:url" content="https://linkzin.net/">
        <meta property="og:site_name" content="Linkzin">
        <meta property="og:type" content="website">
        <meta property="og:image" content="/images/linkzin.png">
        <meta name="author" content="Anderson Bones">
        <meta name="copyright" content="© 2022  Anderson Bones" />

        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/pngegg.png"/>


        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.9.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">


    </head>
    <body>

        <main class="container">
            <%- include('../partials/logo'); %>
            <div class="info text-center mt-4 mb-4">
                <span class="h5 text-muted">Cole a URL para ser encurtada</span>
            </div>
            
            
            <form action="/New" method="post" class="home-form d-flex justify-content-center">
                <input  type="text" name="url" placeholder="Cole o link aqui" required autocomplete="off">
                <button class="btn-pri btn btn-primary d-flex flex-row align-items-center" type="submit">Encurtar <i class="bi bi-link"></i></button>
            </form>

            <article class="home-info text-center mt-5 mb-5">
                <p class="mb-3">O Encurtador de URL permite diminuir um link longo tornando-o fácil de lembrar</p>
                <p>Após encurtar a URL, é possível saber <a class="link" href="/clicks">quantos cliques ela recebeu</a></p>
            </article>

            
        </main>

        <%-include("../partials/footer"); %>

        
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </body>
</html>